        <updating/>
        <source>setCorrectComboStyle() updating;
/*
Purpose:	During the change to 22.0.24 some combo boxes had their STYLE set to zero, this is a patchable way to fix that.				

Date		Who		Reason
11 June 2024	navab1	BUG 64462
